--------------------------------------------------

  Once the threshold is crossed, how fast does performance
  degrade? (Based on Experiment A — FE uncertainty only)

  %VSS > 2%:
    At threshold:      pct_vss = 2.00
    At end of range:   pct_vss = 3.04
    Degradation rate:  7.22 per unit spread
    Rate at +0.05:     7.03 per unit spread

